## 2026-03-29 - useTokenDataLoading stale-closure bug in variables-applied listener
- Fixed stale-closure bug: added `allTokensFlatRef` (useRef) that tracks `allTokensFlat` on every render. The `variables-applied` message handler now reads from the ref instead of closing over the state value. The effect dependency array is now `[]` so the listener is registered once and never torn down/re-added, eliminating the race window where duplicate listeners could fire.
